      "content": "whatever. the goblin thing is just weird. you don't get it. it's not just about the money, it's the fact that i'm a failure. every time i look at my wife i can see her thinking about how much of a loser i am. how am i supposed to live like that? every single day, just waking up to that look on her face and the constant weight of what i've done. it's just a constant, heavy, miserable existence at this point. there's no \"moving forward\" from this level of embarrassment.",
